WEBVTT

0
00:00:05.230 --> 00:00:09.130
NCDITnow is NCDIT's dedicated service management platform.

1
00:00:10.310 --> 00:00:12.689
It brings together how we engage with customers,

2
00:00:12.909 --> 00:00:14.689
how we manage operational work,

3
00:00:14.909 --> 00:00:18.739
and how we maintain visibility into the services that power state government.

4
00:00:18.940 --> 00:00:21.200
Built on modern ServiceNow capabilities,

5
00:00:21.549 --> 00:00:25.219
NCDITnow is designed to support structured processes,

6
00:00:25.549 --> 00:00:27.129
trusted configuration data,

7
00:00:27.350 --> 00:00:29.229
and role-based user experiences.

8
00:00:29.540 --> 00:00:31.409
Whether you work in IT operations,

9
00:00:31.579 --> 00:00:32.450
service delivery,

10
00:00:32.659 --> 00:00:34.560
or a specialist application area,

11
00:00:34.860 --> 00:00:38.860
NCDITnow provides a unified foundation for how work is captured,

12
00:00:38.939 --> 00:00:40.299
connected and delivered.

13
00:00:43.959 --> 00:00:47.650
NCDITnow supports 3 primary user experiences,

14
00:00:47.849 --> 00:00:49.909
each designed for a specific audience.

15
00:00:50.169 --> 00:00:53.610
Internal NCDIT employees access services and submit

16
00:00:53.610 --> 00:00:56.029
requests through the NCDIT Employee Center.

17
00:00:56.369 --> 00:00:57.909
State and local government users,

18
00:00:58.049 --> 00:00:59.950
along with constituents and businesses,

19
00:01:00.200 --> 00:01:00.919
interact through our

20
00:01:00.974 --> 00:01:02.455
Government Services Portal —

21
00:01:02.665 --> 00:01:04.775
The NCDIT Support Center —

22
00:01:05.055 --> 00:01:08.694
built on ServiceNow's Public Sector Digital Services capabilities,

23
00:01:08.974 --> 00:01:11.775
Operational and technical teams manage and fulfill work

24
00:01:11.775 --> 00:01:14.444
through role-based workspaces designed to bring records,

25
00:01:14.535 --> 00:01:15.184
tasks,

26
00:01:15.375 --> 00:01:17.875
and related information together in one place.

27
00:01:18.839 --> 00:01:21.680
While these experiences are tailored to different audiences,

28
00:01:21.919 --> 00:01:24.430
they are all powered by the same underlying system,

29
00:01:24.639 --> 00:01:26.540
data model and governance structure,

30
00:01:26.800 --> 00:01:27.989
ensuring that Requests,

31
00:01:28.120 --> 00:01:29.940
Cases and operational work

32
00:01:30.360 --> 00:01:31.599
remain fully connected.

33
00:01:36.169 --> 00:01:36.870
At its core,

34
00:01:37.019 --> 00:01:40.360
NCDITnow organizes work through structured records.

35
00:01:41.169 --> 00:01:41.919
Requests,

36
00:01:42.050 --> 00:01:42.809
Incidents,

37
00:01:43.089 --> 00:01:43.720
Cases,

38
00:01:44.050 --> 00:01:44.709
Changes,

39
00:01:44.930 --> 00:01:45.919
and Problems

40
00:01:46.089 --> 00:01:48.150
are captured as records within the platform,

41
00:01:48.650 --> 00:01:50.089
each with defined ownership,

42
00:01:50.199 --> 00:01:51.769
status and relationships.

43
00:01:53.059 --> 00:01:55.660
These records are associated to service offerings,

44
00:01:55.900 --> 00:01:58.779
which define the services NCDIT provides

45
00:01:58.980 --> 00:02:02.919
and establish clear accountability through service owners and their teams.

46
00:02:03.139 --> 00:02:04.360
Records are linked to

47
00:02:04.540 --> 00:02:07.139
configuration items within the CMDB

48
00:02:07.419 --> 00:02:10.288
providing visibility into the infrastructure and

49
00:02:10.288 --> 00:02:12.000
applications that support each service.

50
00:02:12.380 --> 00:02:16.009
Tasks are assigned to the users and groups responsible for investigation,

51
00:02:16.179 --> 00:02:16.919
fulfillment,

52
00:02:16.979 --> 00:02:17.820
and resolution.

53
00:02:18.250 --> 00:02:20.679
Because these relationships are structured and governed,

54
00:02:20.929 --> 00:02:22.440
work is not isolated,

55
00:02:22.649 --> 00:02:23.630
it is connected,

56
00:02:23.850 --> 00:02:25.110
enabling reporting,

57
00:02:25.289 --> 00:02:26.350
traceability,

58
00:02:26.529 --> 00:02:29.070
and informed decision making across teams.

59
00:02:30.889 --> 00:02:31.750
Within the platform,

60
00:02:32.050 --> 00:02:35.429
this structure is supported by a govern configuration foundation.

61
00:02:35.729 --> 00:02:37.470
The DIT-owned CMDB

62
00:02:37.770 --> 00:02:40.520
provides a reliable view of how services are defined,

63
00:02:40.850 --> 00:02:42.869
supported and owned across the enterprise.

64
00:02:43.979 --> 00:02:46.839
Services are organized with structured relationships,

65
00:02:46.940 --> 00:02:49.919
connecting them to the specific offerings through which they are delivered.

66
00:02:51.009 --> 00:02:52.770
When operational work is created,

67
00:02:52.949 --> 00:02:54.570
such as Incidents and Requests,

68
00:02:54.779 --> 00:02:58.570
they are categorized against these defined services and offerings,

69
00:02:58.800 --> 00:03:00.779
ensuring consistency in reporting,

70
00:03:01.139 --> 00:03:01.960
accountability

71
00:03:02.179 --> 00:03:03.559
and service visibility.

72
00:03:03.779 --> 00:03:06.759
This enables us to provide customers with clear visibility

73
00:03:06.899 --> 00:03:09.479
into the status of services through our portals.

75
00:03:10.049 --> 00:03:13.750
Because configuration data is structured and maintained centrally,

76
00:03:14.169 --> 00:03:17.729
reporting and service level visibility remain consistent across teams.

77
00:03:17.970 --> 00:03:19.669
The result is transparency,

78
00:03:19.889 --> 00:03:20.869
traceability,

79
00:03:21.089 --> 00:03:22.550
and informed decision making

80
00:03:22.809 --> 00:03:25.789
without requiring manual reconciliation across systems.

81
00:03:29.589 --> 00:03:33.320
User identities are automatically provisioned into NCDITnow

82
00:03:33.320 --> 00:03:36.589
from authoritative identity sources using secure integration.

83
00:03:36.830 --> 00:03:39.160
Access to applications and workspaces

84
00:03:39.389 --> 00:03:42.429
is governed through structured role-based permissions,

85
00:03:42.630 --> 00:03:45.649
ensuring the right people see the right tools and data.

86
00:03:46.919 --> 00:03:50.399
The All menu displays the applications assigned to your role.

87
00:03:52.470 --> 00:03:55.970
Tailored workspaces are available through the Workspaces menu.

88
00:03:56.429 --> 00:03:57.940
For most operational users,

89
00:03:58.190 --> 00:04:01.929
Service Operations Workspace serves as the primary working environment.

90
00:04:02.190 --> 00:04:04.179
Access is structured and intentional.

91
00:04:04.350 --> 00:04:06.169
If additional permissions are required,

92
00:04:06.509 --> 00:04:08.929
requests are managed through the ServiceNow platform team.

93
00:04:10.369 --> 00:04:13.479
NCDITnow is designed to simplify how you work.

94
00:04:13.779 --> 00:04:16.329
You do not need to learn every workspace or application,

95
00:04:16.579 --> 00:04:18.480
only the tools aligned to your role.

96
00:04:19.418 --> 00:04:20.488
Your assigned role

97
00:04:20.949 --> 00:04:22.088
determines what you see,

98
00:04:22.428 --> 00:04:23.178
where you work,

99
00:04:23.308 --> 00:04:25.269
and how responsibilities are structured.

100
00:04:26.380 --> 00:04:27.480
Operational work

101
00:04:27.820 --> 00:04:29.619
is connected to defined services,

102
00:04:29.779 --> 00:04:31.359
ownership and visibility

103
00:04:31.700 --> 00:04:32.420
by design.

104
00:04:33.640 --> 00:04:36.170
Role-based training will provide deeper practical

105
00:04:36.170 --> 00:04:38.470
guidance tailored to your responsibilities.

106
00:04:38.809 --> 00:04:41.910
Together these capabilities provide a unified modern platform

107
00:04:42.529 --> 00:04:46.109
designed to support how NCDIT delivers services today

108
00:04:46.329 --> 00:04:48.690
and how it will continue to evolve in the future.
